videos.description: Cartier Diarra hits a corner 3 to give Kansas State its first lead of the game with under a minute left in the 1st half.
videos.headline: Kansas State takes first lead in final minute of half

videos.description: Jeriah Horne spins between defenders for an impressive toss in, giving Tulsa the 1-point lead over Kansas State.
videos.headline: Horne spins to the rim to put Tulsa ahead

videos.description: Fans rush the court as Tulsa upsets No. 16 Kansas State after a missed opportunity on the game's final possession.
videos.headline: Crowd storms floor as Tulsa upsets No. 16 Kansas State
